#mermaid.live code
#This has to be improved as it's not taking into account the pressure

flowchart TD
    %% Start
    Start([Start / Home Position]) --> PrePick

    %% Pre-pick
    PrePick[/MoveJ to Pre-Pick Position/]

    %% Approach pickup
    PrePick --> ApproachPick[/"MoveL to Pickup Point"/]

    %% Pick object
    ApproachPick --> CloseGripper{{Confirmation / Close Gripper / Pick Object?}}
 
    CloseGripper --> LiftObject[/Lift Object / Move Up/]

    %% Move to place
    LiftObject --> PrePlace[/Move to Pre-Place Position/]
    PrePlace --> ApproachPlace[/"MoveL to Place Point"/]

    %% Place object
    ApproachPlace --> OpenGripper{{Open Gripper / Release Object?}}

    OpenGripper --> ClearArea[/MoveL Up / Clear Area/]

    %% Return
    ClearArea --> ReturnHome[/Return to Home / Ready for Next Cycle/]

    %% End or Loop
    ReturnHome --> Loop{Repeat Cycle?}
    Loop -->|Yes| PrePick
    Loop -->|No| End([End])
